      <title>总统顾问称尼日利亚需要大幅提高电价</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/nigeria-needs-much-higher-power-prices-president-s-adviser-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚总统博拉·蒂努布的能源特别顾问表示，尼日利亚的电价需要上涨约三分之二，才能反映出供电成本，预计几个月内电价就会上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/nigeria-needs-much-higher-power-prices-president-s-adviser-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 10:15:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
